thread.title_full: Pan-Asian Insurer AIA’s New-Business Value Rises 18% - WSJ

author: Maria Armental
title: Pan-Asian Insurer AIA’s New-Business Value Rises 18%
text:
AIA Group Ltd.’s new-business value, a key measure of insurers’ profitability, rose 18% in the third quarter, driven by its business in China and China’s semiautonomous region of Hong Kong.
The pan-Asian insurer said its new-business value rose to $552 million in the three months ended Aug. 31.
